00:07:16.150 --> 00:07:19.110
I don't see how--

00:07:19.110 --> 00:07:20.620
I'm surprised that
that happened.

00:07:20.620 --> 00:07:24.100
I am surprised, also, a
bit that that was able to--

00:07:24.100 --> 00:07:24.640
yeah.

