I'm surprised that it works--

00:07:40.240 --> 00:07:40.720
AUDIENCE: For someone who--

00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:41.496
CHLOE: --the CIA.

00:07:41.496 --> 00:07:42.460
AUDIENCE: --who
compartmentalizes

00:07:42.460 --> 00:07:43.210
their information.

00:07:43.210 --> 00:07:45.380
CHLOE: Yeah,
compartmentalizes information.

00:07:45.380 --> 00:07:47.505
They were probably-- they
