00:07:56.660 --> 00:08:02.098
And feel like the CIA is
just the worst possible--

00:08:02.098 --> 00:08:02.890
AUDIENCE: Customer?

00:08:02.890 --> 00:08:04.390
CHLOE: Yeah.

00:08:04.390 --> 00:08:05.670
