01:06:56.220 --> 01:06:59.200
And so there's no--

01:06:59.200 --> 01:07:01.530
and it's way different from--

01:07:01.530 --> 01:07:03.697
before you could just get
the Comptons, the Vannevar

01:07:03.697 --> 01:07:05.113
Bush in the room,
